Eventually she ended up at a riverbank where Alysia happened to be fishing one day with her sister Gabrielle. She figured out who the girl was, and took her back to Scynthia where she adopted her and made her Princess of Scynthia.<br>
<br>
Not too long after, Alysia's destiny played out as Samsara and Alysia became one in spirit and sometimes body. It also turned out that Belle was Samsara's daughter Karina. Mother and Daughter were once again reunited and have a bond stronger than any.<br>
<br>
Belle finally changed her name to: Isabella-Karina Evanda-Loire<br>
